name: Alan
description: I am Alan and I am Outreach Director for Coding With A Purpose. (I made this very jank website) I have been in this glorious club since 9th grade. Outside of CWAP, I am programming lead for Team 303, and I run for our school's track team.

name: Ayush
description: Hi everyone! My name is Ayush and I am the president of Coding With A Purpose. I have been in this club since freshman year, joining originally to gain experience in coding projects. This club has now grown to much more than just coding, I have met fascinating people, made lifelong experiences, and gotten to work on incredible meaningful projects. Outside of Coding With A Purpose, I am a member of Team 303 in FRC Robotics and Model UN. In my free time I enjoy listening to music and sleeping although I donâ€™t get a lot.

name: Alexander
description: My name is Alexander and I am in charge of managing our projects and helping teach the club members. I have been interested in programming for many years, and this club has been a great opportunity for me to share my knowledge and help impactful coding projects get made. In my free time I work on electronics projects and bike in nature.

name: Aarnav
description: Hello everyone! My name is Arnav Dedhia and I am an officer in coding with a purpose.    Last year, when I joined the club, I learned many new coding concepts. Even now, this club helps me learn all of the many different sides of coding. Outside of school, I swim on a club team and on the brhs swim team. Also, I enjoy hanging out with my friends
